    text: `<p>Funny, but Moran wasn’t flattering at all. Not his style if he's not at some social high-class event. With JM, he always preferred either to keep silence or to speak straight out. That words in his usual dry but quite literary manner weren’t a compliment; only a simple fact, even when talking of such fantasy stuff.</p>
