    text: `<p>Nervous, quick heartbeat skips a second right along with the first, almost soft touch to the lips. Chaotic fire burning inside devours everything that was there in the head, leaving just some scrappy silent swearings and completely disgraceful yet so yearning desire. Moran can’t help himself opening his lips more, letting JM do whatever he wants. He knew that anyway, from the very beginning of this strange, nasty little game he knew JM would want to fuck his mouth like he used to do once and again.</p>
