pagesData[54] = {
    author: "JM",
    text: `<p>After the noises die down, there's a quiet, wheezy laugh breaking next to Moran's ear, as if there was a madman hiding in the dark, celebrating the final takeover of insanity. Despite the chilling sound of it, the embrace he finds himself in is hot, as JM wraps both arms around him and guides him to the floor, climbing atop to pin him down with the weight of his whole body and lick the grease off Moran's face. Exhausted and still shaky with a post-orgasmic tremor, JM makes them stay like this for a while.</p>
